      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "\"Well, these agitators are just stirring up trouble where there ain't none,\" one might grumble, wiping grease from his chin. \"We got a way of doing things here, and we ain't gonna let some outsiders come in and mess up the natural order.\" Another could chime in, \"It's just business, see? We need folks who know how this town works, and we ain't changing that for nobody.\"",
